text:
Vice President Mike Pence called Chief Justice John Roberts a “disappointment” to conservatives last night.

To the frustration of Republican activists, right-leaning justices have consistently moved left once on the bench, @EmmaOGreen wrote in July. https://t.co/UCeBiJIlEf
